    <item>
      <title>为什么朱利安阿桑奇引渡斗争持续多年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/why-julian-assange-extradition-case-has-taken-so-many-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于他的支持者来说，维基解密联合创始人朱利安·阿桑奇是一位因揭露腐败和战争罪行而受到迫害的烈士。对于其他人来说，他是一个肆无忌惮的黑客，通过发布敏感的国家机密而危及生命。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/why-julian-assange-extradition-case-has-taken-so-many-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国马克龙将在经历一周的动荡后访问新喀里多尼亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/france-s-macron-to-visit-new-caledonia-after-week-of-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙计划访问新喀里多尼亚，此前因拟议的选举投票规则修改而引发的骚乱震动了这个海外领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/france-s-macron-to-visit-new-caledonia-after-week-of-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:06:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克立法者团结一致谴责总理枪击事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/slovak-lawmakers-unite-behind-condemnation-of-premier-s-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克立法者一致支持一项议会决议，谴责枪杀总理罗伯特·菲科，此举旨在平息该国在 5 月 15 日暗杀企图后的政治指责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/slovak-lawmakers-unite-behind-condemnation-of-premier-s-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:04:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基与德国外长讨论防空问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/zelenskiy-discussed-air-defenses-with-german-foreign-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽伦斯基在德国外交部长安娜莱娜·贝尔博克访问基辅期间讨论了德国向乌克兰提供额外防空系统的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/zelenskiy-discussed-air-defenses-with-german-foreign-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国出于政治动机的犯罪激增至有记录以来的最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/german-politically-motivated-crime-surges-to-highest-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，在右翼极端主义和反犹太主义激增的推动下，德国出于政治动机的犯罪数量升至近四分之一个世纪以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/german-politically-motivated-crime-surges-to-highest-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大通胀放缓至2.7%，增加6月降息可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/canada-inflation-slows-to-2-7-core-eases-further</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大核心通胀年率连续第四个月下降，为政策制定者在未来几个月开始宽松周期提供了依据，但月度增速的小幅上升可能会使 6 月份降息成为必然。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/canada-inflation-slows-to-2-7-core-eases-further</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 12:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国谴责科索沃警察突袭塞尔维亚银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/us-decries-kosovo-police-raid-on-serbian-bank-as-tensions-simmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和欧盟谴责科索沃警方对塞尔维亚当地一家银行的突袭，称此次行动没有与西方盟友协调，并加剧了该地区本已酝酿的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/us-decries-kosovo-police-raid-on-serbian-bank-as-tensions-simmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 12:26:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱抨击西班牙全面撤回大使是“巨大错误”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/spain-to-fully-withdraw-ambassador-from-argentina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马德里从这个南美国家完全撤回特使后，西班牙和阿根廷之间的外交争端进一步恶化，总统哈维尔·米莱谴责这一举动是愚蠢的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/spain-to-fully-withdraw-ambassador-from-argentina</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 11:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普审判转向辩护，判决结果无人猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/trump-prosecutors-delivered-but-verdict-is-still-anyone-s-guess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过四个星期多的证据收集，曼哈顿检察官于周一结束了针对唐纳德·特朗普的封口费案，这些证据基本上克服了人们对美国前总统首次刑事审判的最初疑虑，尽管案件的结果是谁都在猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/trump-prosecutors-delivered-but-verdict-is-still-anyone-s-guess</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟批准使用冻结俄罗斯资产所得利润的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/eu-approves-plan-to-use-the-profits-from-frozen-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟成员国周二批准了一项计划，利用冻结的俄罗斯主权资产产生的利润支持乌克兰的复苏和军事防御。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/eu-approves-plan-to-use-the-profits-from-frozen-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:30:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
